Well it's Fallout made by Bethesda it's a good game this and that blah blah blah go read some other detailed review because I'm gonna keep it short;

THE GAME ♥♥♥♥♥ CRASH EVERY 1-2 HOURS. AND also randomly crash when you alt+tab.
So, why did I give it a positive review? Honestly I don't really like it that much, AI and actual combat (I mean the actual gun fight, not including VATS) , well, sucks. Bethresda style. But everything else is good.
And Steam has a huge [Notice] in store page;
Fallout 3 is not optimized for Windows 7 and later."
So you better believe it."

